<h2 id="crane-remote-control-simulation-application">Crane Remote Control Simulation application</h2>
<p><strong>Company</strong>: <a href="http://quantize-world.com/">PocketQueries</a>
<strong>Year</strong>: 2018</p>

<p>This is a prototype simulation app using Oculus Rift and Haptic device, 3D mouse to control the crane remotely. The purpose of this app is not for business but for research and exhibition.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Working directly with client engineer to implement the IK system for the crane simulation</li>
  <li>Working with design team to optimize and create rigging structure of the harnesses model so that it can be break when apply force. This is also use for the simulation process.</li>
  <li>Fix and modified haptic plugin to make it working with Unity
