<p>I am currently involved in a project collaborating with a dedicated Vietnam-based outsourcing team. Together, we are working on a prototype production in partnership with the Tokyo Electric Group to create a mixed-reality (MR) experience for working in hazardous environments.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Research and understand low level API of the <a href="https://github.com/FreeRDP/FreeRDP">FreeRDP</a> library.</li>
  <li>Research, Implement and testing with Hololens 1.</li>
  <li>Working and Bridge engineer, take responsibility to make the communication between client and development team smooth. Also do task management for Vietnam team.</li>
</ul>

